review_data.title: SOOOO GOOD
review_data.content: This restaurant is inexpensive for Switzerland and is really good quality. The owner is super nice and checked up on us more than once. My boyfriend got the wings and burger and I got the chicken tenders and we both loved it.

review_data.title: Tasty burger and a very friendly owner
review_data.content: We had a hamburger, fried chicken and a kebab and they were all absolutely delicious. There was also enough space and the locale is very easily accessible. The owner was so friendly too and even gave us a free tea! 10/10 would go again!
